               <p>WILLIAM STONE. I am a <rs id="t18311020-216-viclabel1157" type="occupation">servant</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18311020-216-victim1444 t18311020-216-viclabel1157"></join>. I was in <placeName id="t18311020-216-crimeloc1158">St. James'-park</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18311020-216-crimeloc1158" type="placeName" value="St. James'-park"></interp>
